# CI Workflow Rules

## Path References
- Scripts live at `work/scripts/` (symlinked as `scripts/` at root)
- Tools live at `work/tools/`
- App code is at `apps/avrai_app/lib/` and `apps/avrai_app/test/` (NOT root `lib/` or `test/`)
- Packages are at `shared/avrai_core`, `runtime/avrai_network` (NOT `packages/`)

## Working Directory
- Steps that run `flutter test`, `flutter build`, or reference `lib/`/`test/` must use `working-directory: apps/avrai_app`
- Steps that run repo-level scripts (`dart run scripts/...`, `python3 scripts/...`) should run from repo root

## Package Name
- The package name is `avrai`, NOT `spots`. Use `package:avrai/...` in all references.

## Path Triggers
- Use `apps/avrai_app/lib/**` and `apps/avrai_app/test/**` in path triggers
- Include `engine/**`, `runtime/**`, `shared/**` for monorepo coverage
